description:
Metro Station is the self-titled debut album by pop rock group Metro Station. The album was released on September 18, 2007, via Columbia/Red Ink. As of September 2008, four singles have been released. So far, "Shake It" and "Seventeen Forever" have [2] charted on Billboard charts. The album debuted at #189 on the U.S. Billboard 200, but reached a peak of #39 in June of 2008. The song "Shake It", has been certified Platinum. Since its release, Metro Station has sold approximately 400,000 copies in the United States.
